                  </hi>. I am a merchant, and live in Tooley-street. On the 21st of April I was walking through Little East Cheap—somebody came behind me, and said my pocket had been picked—I missed my hand<lb></lb>Kerchief—I went back, and saw the prisoner in custody—Cuthbert pro<lb></lb>duced the handkerchief—it is mine.</p>
